        "sanitize": false,
        "text": "<div id=\"form-element-wrapper_25\" class=\"formFieldWrapper  static-html-wrapper style-selector_25\" data-field-code=\"\" aria-hidden=\"false\">\n<div class=\"form-static-html form-item\">\n<p><strong>Organic Crop Application:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>Please fill out this form if you are requesting organic farm/crop certification. Use additional sheets if necessary. Sign this form. You must submit farm maps and field history sheets with this application/plan. Attach all other supporting documents (soil, tissue or water tests, rented or recently purchased land histories, etc.) as required.</p>\n<p>Please contact us&nbsp;if you have any additional questions.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"form-section-buttons\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"form-section-buttons\">Complete the following Application and include the supporting documentation as listed when submitting your application.</div>\n<div class=\"form-section-buttons\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div class=\"form-section-buttons\"><strong>Press Next to Continue to begin the application.</strong></div>",
